        "TileImage": "$($repository 61385660-3dc2-4560-a62a-5212e0560b18).Image",
        "Description": "A crumpled note written by HOA homeowner Susan Wilson,\r\rTo Jose Alvarez or whomever it may concern,\r\r&quot;I am SICK of these rodents ruining my home!\r\rThese men stand around the party with weapons, freaking out MY guests!\r\rAnd there&apos;s a bilge rat who&apos;s tainted our park! My young one can&apos;t even play there anymore! It&apos;s horrid!\r\rAnd that BITCH of the Troutt family, rummaging through my son&apos;s stuff with \rher dumb husband. Make sure she gets preferential treatment.\r\rHer cheese dish tastes like vermin.&quot;",
        "GameVersion": "8.22.0.0",
